markets.title: Will Taylor Swift release another album this year?
markets.rules_primary: If Taylor Swift releases another album on Spotify before Jan 1, 2026, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
**For the purposes of this market, The Life of a Showgirl (scheduled for release on October 3, 2025) does not count toward resolution. Resolution depends on whether Taylor Swift releases another album before the Expiration Date.

To qualify, the release must appear as a separate album entry under Taylor Swift’s “Albums” section on Spotify. Deluxe editions, extended versions, or bonus-track albums qualify only if they are released as distinct albums, not merely updates to an existing album entry. Singles, previews, EPs, compilations, and live albums do not qualify.**
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
